'use strict';
module.exports = {
  style: new Set(['italic', 'oblique']),
  variant: new Set(['small-caps']),
  weight: new Set([
    '100',
    '200',
    '300',
    '400',
    '500',
    '600',
    '700',
    '800',
    '900',
    'bold',
    'lighter',
    'bolder',
  ]),
  stretch: new Set([
    'ultra-condensed',
    'extra-condensed',
    'condensed',
    'semi-condensed',
    'semi-expanded',
    'expanded',
    'extra-expanded',
    'ultra-expanded',
  ]),
  size: new Set([
    'xx-small',
    'x-small',
    'small',
    'medium',
    'large',
    'x-large',
    'xx-large',
    'larger',
    'smaller',
  ]),
};
